''why did you leave Positive Head?''

The contract wrapped up, and we iterated on the long term plans for the app. We ended up agreeing the scope of work to integrate video streaming with blockchain techs, along with the legal uncertainties posed a fair amount of risk for the business case. And he was beginning to produce a travel TV series so it just didn't feel right to double down on the effort at that time.
